---
import Title from "../Shared/Title.astro";
import Contact from "../Shared/Contact.astro";
import Marquee from "./Marquee.astro";
import Section from "../Shared/Section.astro";
---

<div class="md:mt-28 my-10 space-y-6">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed">
      I’m a Full-Stack Software Engineer based in Berlin, specializing in
      frontend development with a passion for startups and SaaS products.
    </p>

    <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed">
      I have a strong interest in innovation and enjoy exploring new
      technologies within the JavaScript ecosystem, including Next.js,
      TypeScript, Tailwind, and Supabase.
    </p>

    <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed">
      Currently working as a Product Engineer at
      <a
        href="https://handly.de"
        class="hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-primary transition-all duration-300"
      >
        handly.de
      </a>. I previously worked as a Full-Stack Developer at
      <a
        href="https://www.otto.de"
        class="hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-primary transition-all duration-300"
      >
        Otto.de
      </a>, as a Frontend Developer at
      <a
        href="https://www.nosto.com"
        class="hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-primary transition-all duration-300"
      >
        Nosto
      </a>, as Software Engineer at the Volkswagen Group during my studies and
      collaborated with the Matters of Activity research cluster from Humboldt
      University for my thesis.
    </p>
  </div>

  <Contact />
</div>
